QuestDescription.SourceString: Doric is looking for rare weapons in Fellhollow.
QuestDescription.LocalizedString: Doric is looking for rare weapons in Fellhollow.

Value.SourceString: Craft an Undead Ranger's Bow and bring it to Doric in Fellhollow. Doric believes the recipe is in a vault somewhere.
Value.LocalizedString: Craft an Undead Ranger's Bow and bring it to Doric in Fellhollow. Doric believes the recipe is in a vault somewhere.

Value.SourceString: Craft a Shadow Sword and bring it to Doric in Fellhollow. Doric believes a zogre has the recipe.
Value.LocalizedString: Craft a Shadow Sword and bring it to Doric in Fellhollow. Doric believes a zogre has the recipe.

Value.SourceString: Craft a Necromancer's Staff and bring it to Doric in Fellhollow. Doric believes the recipe is in a vault somewhere.
